teetime.stage.taskfarm

Interface ITaskFarmDuplicable<I,O>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - Input type of the task farm
    O - Output Type of the task farm
    All Superinterfaces:
    ITransformation<I,O>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Counter, MD5Stage, WordCounter

    public interface ITaskFarmDuplicable<I,O>
extends ITransformation<I,O>
    Any AbstractStage or CompositeStage implementing this interface can be used by a Task Farm as an enclosed stage. The enclosed stage may not have more than one input or output port each.
    Author:
    Christian Claus Wiechmann
